      "updated_at": "2016-06-02 23:17:35 UTC",
      "body": "I agree it would be a cool feature to insert type inferences and fill in implicit conversions. I am personally interested in expanding underscore imports.\r\n\r\nHowever, scalafmt doesn't have the semantic information to implement this feature. Same reason #188 won't work."
    }
